## Component Hierarchy

Components are layered from generic to specific. A component should only import from the same level or lower.

```
Pages / Route Segments    (src/app/ or src/pages/)
       |
       v
  Layout Components       (src/components/layout/)
  [Header, Sidebar, PageShell, Breadcrumbs]
       |
       v
  Feature Components      (src/components/features/)
  [UserTable, InvoiceCard, ProductForm]
       |
       v
  UI / Primitive Components  (src/components/ui/)
  [Button, Input, Badge, Dialog, DataTable]
```

**Rule:** Feature components can compose UI components. UI components must not import feature components. Pages import layout and feature components.

