{% if use_i18n %}
## Internationalisation (i18n)

**Library:** next-intl

```
src/
├── i18n/
│   ├── config.ts           # locales, defaultLocale
│   ├── request.ts          # next-intl server config
│   └── routing.ts          # createNavigation helpers
├── messages/
│   ├── en.json             # English strings
│   └── fr.json             # French strings (example)
└── middleware.ts           # locale detection and redirect
```

**Conventions:**
- All user-visible strings go through `useTranslations()` or `getTranslations()`.
- Message keys follow dot notation: `common.save`, `users.table.empty`.
- Never hardcode UI copy in JSX.

{% endif %}

